AUDIO: 'Shadien 2 is here and it is looking very cool. It fixes the two biggest complaints that people have had about Shadienne. The first one being that all apps have started to look the same and the second one that it uses Radix UI components which have largely been abandoned. So let\'s just jump straight'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
