AUDIO: 'this, we\'re taken to a Shaden customizer. This lets you customize everything now, not just Tailwind classes. You can now pick your component library, your base color, your themes, your icons, fonts, everything like that, and hopefully build out an app that'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
